# ISDE

The InfiSystems Desktop Environment, is a deliberately simplistic X11 DE. 
It is a loosely coupled set of basic components suhc as
A WM, a file manager, session manager and a panel.
The design goal is to remain minimal while allowing the user to add or replace 
components as desired.

## Caveats and Warnings

- It works but it's ugly
- Almost entirely produced by Claude code and a lot of sarcasm directed at said.

